	   <tr><td colspan=2>After review of all the messages I am surprised there is no reference as to spell location...<br>I need 44 level spells and so far have the following...<br>From Butcher Block ring:&nbsp;&nbsp;Banish Summoned, Chloroplast, Drifting Death, Nullify Magic, Resist Disease, Resist Poison, Storm Strength.<br>From Surefall Glade:  Allure of the Wild, Form of the Great Wolf, Savage Spirt.<br>Wish I kept better notes on lesser spells.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>BenThere DonThat</td></tr>
