	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's the spore covered cloak that has wisdom (AC: +5 Wis: +1).<br><br>I'd pick up a Charred Guardian Shield (AC: +10 WIS: +9), Gatorscale Leggings (AC: +7 Wis: +4 HP: +15), Velium Etched Stone Mace 1hb 7/22 (Str: +3 Wis: +3).<br><br>Depending on how good a deal you get for these, you'll have now spent between 1200 and 1500 plat. Either put the rest into jewelry (Plat Jasper rings are WIS: +6 each; Ruby Veils give both STR and WIS) or a chest piece such as a Foreman's Tunic (AC: +10 Str: +3 Wis: +3).<br>&nbsp;<br>-- Ancarett, who lives at <a href="http://ancarett.com" target=_new>http://ancarett.com</a></td></tr>
