	   <tr><td colspan=2>You do not get XP for PvPing, but you may loot one item o' choice (But not if it is in a bag)...<br><br>'Bout the &quot;Best Char&quot;:<br>My experience so far is that there is no such thing as a &quot;Best Char&quot;, it depends on if you wanna be in groups, solo, melee, cast spells etc. (A cleric is a nice addition to any group, but useless as a soloer and a necro is a great soloer, but not the first thing I would wanna have in my group)...<br>But if ya want my opinion; <br>Shadow Knights rules the PvP surver because o' their HT, SS and because o' their great HP (This is just my opinion, though)...<br>Anyway; I choosed the ranger class, 'cause I love track, archery, dual-wield, wood elves, SoW and to role-play (Man, I got in bags, coffers and boxes)...<br><br>Anyway; Be what ya wanna be and enjoy...<br><br>Tiras Whiteleaf<br>&nbsp;<br>May the goddess smile upon you, keep your swords sharp and your sight clear... </td></tr>
